Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_disable...to_data_checks(25.10)  timing_disable...to_data_checks(25.10)

Name
       timing_disable_library_data_to_data_checks

Syntax
       timing_disable_library_data_to_data_checks

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       When  set  to  true,  this global disables data-to-data checks that are
       coded in the library  as  non-sequential  timing  checks.  Data-to-data
       checks  are  distinguished  from other non-sequential timing checks be-
       cause both the reference pin and constrained pin  side  of  the  timing
       check  are  data  pins  rather than clock pins. You should use the tim-
       ing_disable_non_sequential_checks global to control other types of non-
       sequential checks where the reference pin is a clock pin.

       To set this global variable, use the set_global command.

